// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3038 — Mass File Rename (handala)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 6052578e-f2cd-54dc-abe1-0ae01bd56251

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
